WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sq

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Translator: Aida Musai
Reviewer: Helena Bedalli

00:00:12.757 --> 00:00:16.244
259 mije ton

00:00:16.244 --> 00:00:22.551
letra fshirese duarsh

00:00:22.551 --> 00:00:24.438
perdoren nga amerikanet

00:00:24.438 --> 00:00:28.109
cdo vit.

00:00:28.109 --> 00:00:31.164
Nese ne do te... me falni, dhashe shifren e gabuar...

00:00:31.164 --> 00:00:33.515
13 miliarde vete perdorin cdo vit.

00:00:33.515 --> 00:00:36.618
Nese do te kursenim ne perdorimin e letres se duarve,

00:00:36.618 --> 00:00:39.800
me nje leter per cdo person cdo dite,

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:46.681
atehere do te kursenim 259.000 ton leter.

00:00:46.681 --> 00:00:48.816
Ne mund t'a bejme kete.

00:00:48.816 --> 00:00:52.746
Ka disa tipe letra duarsh.

00:00:52.746 --> 00:00:56.977
Eshte ajo e palosur ne tre.
Njerezit marrin dy ose tre prej saj.

00:00:56.977 --> 00:01:01.140
Eshte ajo qe duhet prere, duhet t'a terheqesh.

00:01:01.140 --> 00:01:03.404
Njerezit fillojne, nje, dy, tre, kater, pastaj terheqin.

00:01:03.404 --> 00:01:04.842
Gjithe kete leter, apo jo?

00:01:04.842 --> 00:01:07.307
Eshte ajo qe pritet vete.

00:01:07.307 --> 00:01:11.447
Njerezit fillojne, nje, dy, tre, kater.

00:01:11.447 --> 00:01:15.522
Pastaj kemi po te njejtat tipe,
por me leter te ricikluar,

00:01:15.522 --> 00:01:20.035
dhe sigurisht prej ketyre duhet te marresh pese,
sepse ato nuk thithin mire.

00:01:20.035 --> 00:01:26.556
E verteta eshte se ti mund t'ia dalesh
me nje leter te vetme.

00:01:26.556 --> 00:01:28.596
Celesi? Dy fjale:

00:01:28.596 --> 00:01:33.044
Gjysma ketej e dhomes, fjala juaj eshte "shkund".

00:01:33.044 --> 00:01:35.226
Thuajeni fort. Shkund. Me fort.

00:01:35.226 --> 00:01:36.771
Publiku: Shkund

00:01:36.771 --> 00:01:38.947
Joe Smith: Fjala juaj eshte "palos"

00:01:38.947 --> 00:01:40.063
Publiku: Palos

00:01:40.063 --> 00:01:40.990
JS: Edhe nje here.

00:01:40.990 --> 00:01:43.059
Publiku: Palos. JS: Me fort.

00:01:43.059 --> 00:01:44.607
Publiku: Shkund. Palos

00:01:44.607 --> 00:01:48.767
JS: Okay. Lagim duart.

00:01:48.767 --> 00:01:53.567
Shkund... nje, dy, tre, kater, pese, gjashte, shtate, tete, nente, dhjete, njembedhjete, dymbedhjete.

00:01:53.567 --> 00:01:56.505
Pse 12? Jane dymbedhjete apostuj,
dymbedhjete tribu

00:01:56.505 --> 00:02:00.612
dymbedhjete shenja horoskopi, dymbedhjete muaj.
Dhe e preferuara ime:

00:02:00.612 --> 00:02:02.809
eshte numri me i madh me vetem nje rrokje ne anglisht.

00:02:02.809 --> 00:02:07.071
(te qeshura)

00:02:07.071 --> 00:02:14.431
Letra e palosur ne tre. Palos...

00:02:14.431 --> 00:02:15.983
U thane.

00:02:15.983 --> 00:02:20.215
(duartrokitje)

00:02:20.215 --> 00:02:25.429
Publiku: Shkund.

00:02:25.429 --> 00:02:28.361
Palos.

00:02:28.361 --> 00:02:30.939
JS: Ajo qe pritet vete. Palos.
Palosja eshte e rendesishme

00:02:30.939 --> 00:02:35.821
sepse lejon pezullimin e ndermjetem.

00:02:35.821 --> 00:02:38.299
Kete pjese nuk duhet me doemos t'a kujtoni,
thjesht besojeni.

00:02:38.299 --> 00:02:43.352
(te qeshura)

00:02:43.352 --> 00:02:50.069
Publiku: Shkund. Palos.

00:02:50.069 --> 00:02:55.731
JS: Ajo qe pritet vete.

00:02:55.731 --> 00:02:56.888
Gjeja me argetuese eshte se

00:02:56.888 --> 00:02:59.063
une i thaj duart me mire se ata qe
perdorin tre apo kater letra,

00:02:59.063 --> 00:03:01.511
sepse ata nuk arrijne neper te carat.

00:03:01.511 --> 00:03:04.655
Nese mendoni se kjo nuk eshte aq e mire...

00:03:04.655 --> 00:03:13.124
Publiku: Shkund. Palos.

00:03:13.124 --> 00:03:16.692
JS: Tani ka dale nje shpikje shume moderne

00:03:16.692 --> 00:03:19.099
ajo ku ti leviz duart dhe

00:03:19.099 --> 00:03:20.890
dhe ajo heq ujin.

00:03:20.890 --> 00:03:22.976
Por ajo eshte nje leter kaq e madhe.

00:03:22.976 --> 00:03:24.003
Me lejoni t'ju tregoj nje sekret.

00:03:24.003 --> 00:03:26.090
Nese tregoheni te shpejte, vertet te shpejte...

00:03:26.090 --> 00:03:27.670
dhe une mund t'jua provoj kete...

00:03:27.670 --> 00:03:32.519
kjo eshte gjysma e nje letre nga
makineria ne kete ndertese.

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:35.886
Si behet? Sapo letra te filloje te dale,
ti duhet t'a terheqesh.

00:03:35.886 --> 00:03:37.558
Makina eshte aq e zgjuar sa te ndalet.

00:03:37.558 --> 00:03:41.550
Dhe ti ke vetem gjysme letre.

00:03:41.550 --> 00:03:54.827
Publiku: Shkund. Palos.

00:03:54.827 --> 00:04:01.661
JS: Tani le t'a themi te gjithe bashke.
Shkund. Palos.

00:04:01.661 --> 00:04:05.804
Dhe ju do t'i kujtoni gjithnje keto fjale,

00:04:05.804 --> 00:04:08.787
sa here qe t'ju duhet nje leter duarsh.

00:04:08.787 --> 00:04:13.875
Mos harroni, nje leter per cdo person per cdo vit...

00:04:13.875 --> 00:04:18.595
259.000 ton leter. Nuk eshte pak.

00:04:18.595 --> 00:04:20.843
Ndersa vitin e ardhshem, letra higjenike.

00:04:20.843 --> 00:04:22.219
(te qeshura)

